title: MediaMonkey.Gold.v4.0.2.1462.Multilingual.Incl.Keymaker-CORE
description:
MediaMonkey Gold v4.0.2.1462 Multilingual Incl Keymaker-CORE

MediaMonkey: The Music Organizer for Serious Collectors
Manage small to very large collections of audio files and playlists (50,000+), whether on a hard drive, network, or CDs. Lookup missing information and album art online, tag almost any audio format, and automatically rename/re-organize tracks on your hard drive.


The new version 4.0.2 is a patch update that resolves database upgrade issues to MediaMonkey 4.0.1 which is in itself a minor update that resolves ~40 miscellaneous issues (database upgrades, DLNA media sharing, Art views, tagging, etc.) in MediaMonkey 4.0.
